{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2021/01/07/ReactNative调试时找不到script.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"12252b11-0ee6-5af6-b8b4-43302cd7970a","excerpt":"ReactNative 调试时提示找不到 script 执行以下命令 另外，如果不成功，可以尝试重新安装 react-native-cli 并重复上面命令。","html":"<h1>ReactNative 调试时提示找不到 script</h1>\n<p>执行以下命令</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">react-native bundle --platform android --dev false --entry-file index.js --bundle-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle --assets-dest android/app/src/main/res</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>另外，如果不成功，可以尝试重新安装 react-native-cli 并重复上面命令。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2021/01/07/ReactNative调试时找不到script.html","date":"January 07, 2021","title":"ReactNative调试时找不到script"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2021/01/07/ReactNative调试时找不到script.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2021/01/04/弥留之国的爱丽丝.html","title":"弥留之国的爱丽丝"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tv"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2021/01/07/甜蜜家园.html","title":"甜蜜家园"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tv"}}}}}